# MongoDB HA Cluster Infrastructure

This directory contains all Kubernetes manifests for the MongoDB HA cluster deployment:

- `operator-values.yaml` - Helm values for Percona MongoDB Operator
- `mongodb-cluster.yaml` - PerconaServerMongoDB custom resource
- `mongodb-secrets-sealed.yaml` - Sealed secrets for MongoDB credentials
- `mongodb-encryption-key-sealed.yaml` - Sealed encryption key
- `mongodb-loadbalancer.yaml` - MetalLB LoadBalancer service
- `mongodb-servicemonitor.yaml` - Prometheus ServiceMonitor
- `mongodb-alerts.yaml` - PrometheusRule for alerting

The ArgoCD Application manifest is located at `bootstrap/components/mongodb.yaml`.
